MC-109055.message: Large Cocoa Pod texture is inconsistent
MC-109055.description:
=>MC-109055
*The Bug:*

Large cocoa pod top texture is only 7 pixels wide, while the sides are 8 pixels wide. The cocoa pod doesn't also have a consistent texture consistency. It varies from the sides of the pod to the top/bottom of the pod.

*--------------------------------------*

*Steps on how to reproduce:*

*1.* _Equip;_ cocoa beans, bonemeal and jungle logs, place 2 jungle logs down vertically and then plant some cocoa beans on the side of the already place down jungle logs.

*2.* _Bonemeal_ the cocoa pod until it grows to a large cocoa pod. (Max size and looks brownish).

*3.* _Count_ the pixels of the cocoa pod's horizontal and vertical sides.

*--------------------------------------*
